parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lower ball joint can cause the wheel to come off the vehicle, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle's wheel comes off while driving
the ball joint breaks or snaps
the vehicle is difficult to control
a rubbing noise occurs when making a turn

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of recall repairs can lead to repeat failures of the lower ball joint, causing the wheel to come off the vehicle, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The recall repair was not performed
the dealer did not fix the issue
the ball joint failed again after recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate warranty coverage can leave vehicle owners with costly repairs, leading to financial burdens and potential safety risks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or die, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. It can also cause fires, which can result in serious injury or damage.

The failure of the ignition coil pack can cause the vehicle to stall suddenly, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
